overview: A medieval girl stands at the edge of a clifftop. Behind her, a gaunt castle, the Lord who has claimed her for his wife, and the cruel execution of her lover. Before her, cold dark waves. She leaps. As she falls through the waters, her long dress blooms out around her. She lets out her last breath. Even as her vision blurs, she catches a glimpse of his faceâ€¦
title: The Underwater Realm - Part IV - 1208
